# Memory Rules

- Before broad repo exploration, read `.memory/project-map.md`.
- Read `.memory/architecture.md` and `.memory/current-state.md` when the task touches system design or current implementation status.
- After structural changes, update the relevant `.memory/` files in the same change.
- Append important architectural choices to `.memory/decisions.md`.
- Keep memory concise, factual, and easy for future agents to scan quickly.
